        <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-4 leading-tight">Brand without product is decoration.</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
          A new logo and palette don't change how customers understand a company.
          Repositioning happens on the pages where customers form opinions, not
          in the brand book.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="lesson-card">
        <div class="linocut-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="14" y="14" width="52" height="52" fill="#E13D0F" stroke="#02101D" stroke-width="3"/>
