            <circle cx="53" cy="53" r="4" fill="#02101D"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-4 leading-tight">Triage protects the launch.</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
          You can't rewrite 150 pages. Naming which ones do strategic work and
          which ones just move forward is what makes a launch feasible. Without
          triage, the work stalls in scope.
